text: Neubrandenburg Airport is a public, general aviation airport and former military airbase located north-east of Neubrandenburg in Trollenhagen, Mecklenburg-Vorpommern, Germany. ==See also== * Transport in Germany * List of airports in Germany ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:Air Forces of the National People's Army Neubrand Category:German airbases
